How to get a nodeserver into your localhost website:

enter the exapp repo in the tritech cyber security repos

copy the url

enter the terminal

type 'git clone (the exapp repo name)

type cd exapp

there is a debug npm command in one of the files

type 'more code_to_start_node.txt'

there will be the npm command

copy the shown command

the port available for the nodeserver is port 3000

if need more instructions or another 'how to' for your localhost
please enter it in the comments below.
